# Skills Directory

This directory contains your custom skills that Waldemar can utilize.

## Creating a New Skill

To add a new skill, create a subdirectory with a `SKILL.md` file:

```bash
mkdir -p skills/my-skill-name
cat > skills/my-skill-name/SKILL.md << 'EOF'
# My Tactical Skill

Brief description of what this skill provides.

## Usage

Reference this skill with: /skill:my-skill-name

## Details

More detailed explanation...
EOF
```

Then reload Waldemar:
```
/reload
```

## Example Skills to Consider

- `siege-tactics` — Architectural design patterns
- `debugging-protocols` — Systematic problem-solving approaches
- `deployment-ceremony` — Release and deployment strategies
- `security-standards` — Defensive coding practices
- `performance-optimization` — Efficiency and optimization techniques

